{"type": "article", "id": 10294, "title": "Vadolibero 自行车架", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-02T07:15:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235437N3WkpHKnlXSjLCgx.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">意大利设计公司 Vadolibero 致力于在全世界推广自行车文化，他们最近推出了一款自行车架，专门为喜欢木工的骑行者设计。木架采用立式结构，带有多个单元格子抽屉，既能存放自行车，又能对不同的物品进行归类收纳，甚至连存放钥匙，眼镜等小物品的地方都被分门别类设计。而顶层托盘则可以满足充电需求。<a href=\"http://vadolibero.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是官方主页</a>，点击可以差多详细信息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235433QL0ayqDGI1nSYJKu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235433FJrDMBnHsWEZNcoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235433W20uFz3hJLsbrcU4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235434jYmK7xzGlNw0PnaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235434EVCzeNRpdr1FaLqI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354351WL8la3ewRpQHF4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235435hCWRKP0LjetN3Gui.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235436KvSQabUM2uHIOT10.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235436K3q12YAcUSL7lzua.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=